preference.name: TCAA113_DWFX_by_publish_override_generation_params
preference.preference_description: Drives the behavior about page setup settings used to generate DWFx files via PUBLISH command. This option is taken into consideration only if TCAA113_DWFX_generation_mode is set to 1. Possible values: 0 - keep current page setup settings (Default) 1 - leave TCAA to force its own page setup settings: plot is centered, scaled to fit to paper and the plot area is set to extents.
